{"id": 2186, "genre": 1000, "title": "现如今，你都如何定义“充实”？", "description": "别人给你贴的“生活空虚”标签通常不怎么靠谱，那么你觉得真正的充实有啥必备条件？（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 20293, "comment_count": 32, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201802211436260sO9nigRQPzwTACK.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-02-21T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 3761, "title": "现如今，你都如何定义“充实”？", "content": "现如今，你都如何定义“充实”？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 265940, "content": "总体上认同自己学习、工作的价值，而不是盲目混日子", "image": "img/option/option/20180221174020sfRSjNtpzvFo69Uw.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 265941, "content": "闲暇时间有自己的业余爱好，放松的时候也能尽兴玩", "image": "img/option/option/20180221174228fIdEtZi0rvpWnHX5.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 265942, "content": "不勉强自己去不喜欢的活动聚会，在无谓社交上花时间", "image": "img/option/option/201802211744040yijDzWM3H2hpaU1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 265943, "content": "做事之前有明确的目标和计划，一步一个脚印", "image": "img/option/option/2018022117445819bqSdkRtIyH5fW4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 265944, "content": "有基本的时间管理技能，大部分时候不被拖延症困扰", "image": "img/option/option/20180221175051MecXjBgJPR9lyKqD.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 265945, "content": "隔段时间工作生活会有变化或改善，而不是一直重复", "image": "img/option/option/201802211751280PLiIBwG1DeZ7Flr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 265946, "content": "对“获取新知”感兴趣，精神上不自我封闭", "image": "img/option/option/20180221175243xmqZ8fHAkiVGL62r.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 265947, "content": "专注自己要做的事情而不是被周围世界影响、盲从流行", "image": "img/option/option/20180221175528UrSB6khseVyHPzT3.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}